flowchart LR
  Version[Approved Page Version] --> Agent[Deployment Agent]
  Agent --> Plan[Release Plan]
  Plan --> Checks[Preflight Checks]
  Checks --> Decision{Blockers?}
  Decision -- Yes --> Blocked[BLOCKED]
  Decision -- No --> Approved[Approved Deploy]
  Approved --> Deploy[Deploy Worker]
  Deploy --> Netlify[Netlify Deploy]
  Netlify --> Verify[Verification Worker]
  Verify --> Health{Healthy?}
  Health -- Yes --> Live[LIVE_HEALTHY]
  Health -- No --> Rollback[ROLLBACK_RECOMMENDED]

